# =====================================================================
# .gitignore — Marketplace Catalog Integrity & Return Analytics
# Analytics Engineering repository. Source (SQL, Python, YAML, Markdown,
# and the Bronze/Silver sample data) is versioned; generated artifacts are not.
# =====================================================================

# ---- Python ----
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
.venv/
venv/
env/
.mypy_cache/
.pytest_cache/
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# ---- Editors / IDE ----
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp

# ---- OS ----
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# ---- Local tooling ----
.claude/

# ---- Generated artifacts (reproducible from source) ----
# The Gold database and its exports are rebuilt by scripts/build_gold.py and
# scripts/export_gold.py — never committed.
gold.duckdb
*.duckdb.wal
data/03_gold/

# Machine-readable run reports are regenerated on every build; the Markdown
# reports are kept as committed evidence.
docs/*.json

# ---- Temporary exports / logs / scratch ----
*.log
logs/
tmp/
scratch/
scratchpad/
*.tmp
*.bak

# =====================================================================
# Intentionally KEPT (do not ignore):
#   data/01_bronze/    - raw sample data (source of truth for the pipeline)
#   data/02_silver/    - cleaned sample data (reproducible, but kept as a sample)
#   sql/, src/, config/, scripts/   - all pipeline source
#   docs/*.md          - specifications & run reports (Markdown)
#   *.pbix             - Power BI dashboard file, once built (a deliverable)
# =====================================================================
